primaryHost.about:
Welcome to Spa City Rentals. Located in Hot Springs Arkansas. 

We absolutely love hosting vacation rental homes for guests! We love meeting new people & always learning new things! We go above and beyond for our guests. We are local & very hands on with all our properties. We are the owners of the homes as well.

We have always loved Hot Springs. All the antique shops, Lake Hamilton, all the restaurants, breweries and Oaklawn of course!
